      <description>&lt;p&gt;本文根据&lt;a href=&#34;https://huggingface.co/learn/agents-course/unit2/smolagents/introduction&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;Hugging Face上的Agent课程&lt;/a&gt;编写而成，包括        。&#xA;相关资源：&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://huggingface.co/docs/smolagents&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;smolagents Documentation&lt;/a&gt; - Official docs for the smolagents library&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.anthropic.com/engineering/building-effective-agents&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;Building Effective Agents&lt;/a&gt; - Research paper on agent architectures&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://huggingface.co/docs/smolagents/tutorials/building_good_agents&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;Agent Guidelines&lt;/a&gt; - Best practices for building reliable agents&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://langchain-ai.github.io/langgraph/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;LangGraph Agents&lt;/a&gt; - Additional examples of agent implementations&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/function-calling?api-mode=chat&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;Function Calling Guide&lt;/a&gt; - Understanding function calling in LLMs&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.pinecone.io/learn/retrieval-augmented-generation/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;RAG Best Practices&lt;/a&gt; - Guide to implementing effective RAG&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://huggingface.co/blog/smolagents&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;smolagents Blog&lt;/a&gt; - Introduction to smolagents and code interactions&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;什么是smolagents为什么要使用smolagents&#34;&gt;什么是smolagents，为什么要使用smolagents？&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;smolagents 是一个 &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/huggingface/smolagents&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreffer &#34;&gt;Hugging Face 库&lt;/a&gt;。smolagents 是一个简单但功能强大的 AI 代理构建框架。它为LLM提供了与现实世界交互的能力，例如搜索或生成图像。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
